text: Þis is þæra fif hida landboc.
Þæ Eadgar cing gebocade Ælfweard bisceope on æce yrfe.
Ðis synd þa landgemæro to fif hidan ærest to wures byrgylse norð to wæter dellæ to Ælfheres stapole swa norð to Bæhildestoccæ.

Swa forð to Godwines gemære and swa andlang gemæres on Healfheages gemære and swa of Ealfheages gemære on bugan stoc of bugan stoccæ on þa haran apoldre on blacan grafas to fif beorgan of fif beorgan on þa mæde of þære mæde<../images/tbar.gif>eft to þan byrigelse.
